column1: Dinodas Brandybuck was a Hobbits of the Shire.
Dinodas was the sixth child and youngest son of Gorbadoc Brandybuck and Mirabella Took. He attended Bilbo Baggins Bilbos Farewell Party.

column2: Dodinas is a Celtic name of unknown meaning. Dodynas and Dinodes are both alternate spellings of the Table Knight Sir Dodinas le Savage.Christopher W. Bruce (ed.)
